{"title":"诗三首","authors":["苏金伞"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏金伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼之乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄子：“涸辙之鲋，相濡以沫，不如相忘于江湖”——江湖，乃自由也。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场大水漫过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辙里留下两条小鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辙水干了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条小鱼各自用口沫濡湿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相依为命片刻难离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一场大水冲来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把两条小鱼冲入大河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此再也没见过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记了对方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也忘记了自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鱼失去了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却得到了天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄子也感到鱼之乐了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“庄周梦为蝴蝶，栩栩然蝴蝶也”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双大翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着极其鲜奇的颜色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着极其美丽的花纹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在微风拂弄的花枝间轻轻扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一扇动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都漾溢出自由、舒徐、和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的色调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都闪现出栩栩然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄周的梦为蝴蝶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是为了这个“栩栩然”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不就成为“涸辙之鱼”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好“自濡以沫”了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独轮车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独轮车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在霜地上轧出一道辙迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的车辙远远地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逝去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送走了时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不见回还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳沿着车辙滚了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越升越高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人以更广阔的风景。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}